description: Luckiest Guy is a friendly heavyweight sans-serif font inspired by custom hand lettered 1950's advertisements. Large and in charge, this offbeat, lovably legible font lends itself to all sorts of uses. Take Luckiest Guy for a spin and let him pack a punch for both your website and your design work.
